OL,3,CSpike in vandalism prompts call to
OL,4,Cprotect historic sites
OL,6,FA surge in vandalism has seen
OL,7,Fresidents living near some of Wales's
OL,8,Fmost treasured historic landmarks
OL,9,Furged to stay alert.
OL,11,FAncient monuments, castles, and listed
OL,12,Fbuildings have become increasingly
OL,13,Ftargeted by unlawful activity which
OL,14,Finclude graffiti, break-ins, and anti-
OL,15,Fsocial behaviour, sparking concern
OL,16,Famong heritage authorities and
OL,17,Fgovernment officials.
