OL,3,CSpike in vandalism prompts call to
OL,4,Cprotect historic sites
OL,6,FSince the beginning of the year,
OL,7,Fmultiple incidents of criminal damage
OL,8,Fhave been reported by Cadw, the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment's historic environment
OL,10,Fservice, leading to closures,
OL,11,Femergency repairs, and the
OL,12,Fpostponement of planned conservation
OL,13,Fwork at several major sites.
OL,15,FNeath Abbey is among the sites
OL,16,Faffected, having experienced a spate
OL,17,Fof incidents in recent months.
