OL,3,CSpike in vandalism prompts call to
OL,4,Cprotect historic sites
OL,6,FMeanwhile, ongoing issues at
OL,7,FCaerleon's Roman Amphitheatre and
OL,8,FBarracks have included graffiti, fire
OL,9,Fdamage from barbecues, repeated
OL,10,Fmasonry vandalism, and even the
OL,11,Fdiscovery of a burnt-out motorbike
OL,12,Fleft among the ruins. The damage has
OL,13,Fforced Cadw stonemasons to divert
OL,14,Fefforts from conservation to emergency
OL,15,Frepairs.
OL,17,FOfficials are encouraging anyone who
OL,18,Fwitnesses or suspects such crimes to
OL,19,Freport them immediately.
